{"tid":2427800,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人/移民香港人/回流香港人/台灣人 等緊你入嚟","createTime":"2021-03-01T05:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T14:24:30.000Z","uid":9178,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3efed4c6eafcf243adeaf1060c23cd72b85e6ba4","tid":2427800,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T05:15:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">香港人<br />\n喺外國嘅香港人<br />\n回流香港嘅香港人<br />\n台灣人</span><br />\n<br />\n呢個谷都歎迎你 交友無分界限<br />\n<br />\n不論你好悶，係外國冇人傾計，返嚟香港後冇朋友，台灣人想認識香港文化，呢到都十分啱你。<span class=\"orange\">話題圍繞國家，個人，日常生活，總之咩都講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n呢到絕不強逼你出聚，自由出聚。呢到啲<span class=\"gold\">外國巴絲已經自行成功搞過聚啦</span><br />\n<br />\n暫時谷中24小時都有人 因為唔同國家嘅人都有（<span class=\"gold\">歐洲+香港+本地台灣人</span>）<br />\n<br />\n唔洗擔心時差，總有人陪到你<br />\n<br />\nset咗只可填一次 所以要登入 唔想人重複又重複咁填<br />\n如果擔心嘅就唔好入 個人選擇 <br />\n絕對唔會揀人加 所以歡迎入完再入 <br />\n加人速度慢 唔好意思要耐心等等<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">P.s 身處英國嘅谷友強烈表示希望多啲英國jj加入，佢哋等緊你哋入嚟</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/KbEdDZYPmTcz45dt5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FKbEdDZYPmTcz45dt5&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3WrU9%2B1YVtZAf0CByt%2F7qsI%3D&h=da49ee4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/KbEdDZYPmTcz45dt5</a>"},{"pid":"18872a781a55c6f213887f6e95d449639b3d4fca","tid":2427800,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:23:51.000Z","msg":"唔接受入嚟潛水做cd-rom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49764ab1fa1426a626c0e6787760c4ca04b0f9a0","tid":2427800,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37bfebadde1ea98002b15ae64b07a3a231683a08","tid":2427800,"uid":9178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T12:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" cl